                    </a>
                    
                    
                    
                </div>
                <div class="article-entry" itemprop="articleBody">
                    <p>
                        <a class="article-title" href="/post/19-12-22-lamp-driver/"><img width=1000 height=100 alt="Banner" src="/post/19-12-22-lamp-driver//banner.jpg"></a><br>
                    Just a quick and small project, I put an electronic transformer into an enclosure. It&rsquo;s my favorite EuroBox enclosure, front and backpanel were 3D printed.
Update 20.01.2023 I replaced the lamp driver with an old 12V halogen transformer I had sitting around. For further protection I added a polyfuse to the secondary side.
